{"tid":1665521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波羅共識","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T16:03:38.000Z","uid":241240,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7766514eb7993277dd4ac9a308a4ef7719abb285","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"經過咗自己開post (已del post)，再睇左咁多post之後<br />\n發現大家其實對波羅嘅出現仲係未有一個共識<br />\n先勿論今日個假野係狗定手足放，因為就好似火魔法咁<br />\n只要係有用嘅野都會有被普及化嘅可能性<br />\n所以想係未普及前即刻黎個公投，等大家有個共識，究竟係可接受定謝絕<br />\n<br />\n正負皮選項歸納左各種意見，希望無漏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔割<br />\n--&gt; 相信前線手足會有足夠嘅道德觀去判斷引爆時機 (唔殺平民只殺狗)<br />\n--&gt; 波羅甚至可以令RB升級，對前線手足嘅安全有好大幫助<br />\n--&gt; 係運動升級嘅標誌，可作為一種表達<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼: 割<br />\n--&gt; 因為67暴動前車可鑑，波羅一定係弊大於利 (民意逆轉/terrorist labeling)<br />\n--&gt; 運動好有可能因為一個前線手足嘅失誤而輸咗 (uncontrolled risk)<br />\n--&gt; 鬼波羅唔同鬼molotov，因為殺傷力太大分別，控制唔到就不如謝絕波羅<br />\n--&gt; 會成為開真槍嘅借口? (唔肯會唔會，但有ching提過)"},{"pid":"4e6c6ab1fa611a356804f7df3af253d06e208cb8","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"e27a6b4f9d19a3c6f729bb51d888f65cb58b32f0","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"0be967eab1bc20e6f6a64ba72d07bf10c2e280e4","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"ac84eaafb044c08aa2df2b1de045265ad4e5b203","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:13:03.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"4edee433238cb2c4420723fa2b77bca5d5973359","tid":1665521,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"3d3ddf622a35218a1145376e35719fcfe947861d","tid":1665521,"ui